@startuml
|User|
start
: Click on Add products button in Inventory Management screen;
|System|
: Display form to add Product;
|User|
repeat
: Select Product;
: Enter quantity;
repeat while(more product?)
: Click Confirm button;
|System|
: Validate data;
if(Data valid?) then (Yes)
  : Update Product quantity to the database;
  : Add Product receiving information to the database;
  : Update Inventory Management screen;
else (No)
  : Display error message;
end if
stop
@enduml
